421
00:35:44,680 --> 00:35:45,970
What?

422
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:47,770
You don't remember?

423
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:51,270
You ran my car off the road a few nights ago.

424
00:35:51,980 --> 00:35:53,570
Investigators have boot prints,

425
00:35:53,580 --> 00:35:56,870
hair fibers,samples of the mud found
in your apartment.

